ople/Oliver-Anthony-Music/100085643337139/">Oliver Anthony Music</a> on <a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100085643337139/posts/268364846028291/">Monday, September 11, 2023</a></p></blockquote></div><p> “My plate has been full and I delegated the responsibility to someone else to help me book. I am not pointing fingers at Cotton Eyed Joe, I don&#39;t know where the miscommunication took place,” he said.</p><p> “I&#39;m just upset seeing those prices. We will find another place in Knoxville area that can do $25 ticket and free meet and greet. I will work to get your tickets refunded from my own budget if they can&#39;t.这种事永远不会再发生了。谢谢你的耐心。 I am still learning how all of this works.”</p><p> Anthony joined <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/papa-roach">Papa Roach</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shinedown">Shinedown</a> for an <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-oliver-anthony-perform-with-papa-roach-and-shinedown-3495781">acoustic performance of a few songs in a car park at the rain-affected Blue Ridge Rock Festival</a> last Saturday (September 9). They played a cover of Lynyrd Skynyrd&#39;s &#39;Simple Man&#39; as well as Papa Roach&#39;s &#39;Last Resort&#39;.</p><p> Oliver Anthony&#39;s viral hit &#39;Rich Men North Of Richmond&#39; was released on August 8, and has since hit Number One on the iTunes Country Charts, soared to the top spot on Apple Music&#39;s Global Music Charts, and racked up over 32million views on YouTube.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oliver-anthony-cancels-show-over-ticket-price-performs-for-free-with-papa-roach-instead-3497443">Oliver Anthony cancels show over ticket price, performs for free with Papa Roach instead</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 'Frasier' reboot will pay tribute to late John Mahoney https://www.nme.com/news/tv/frasier-reboot-will-pay-tribute-to-late-john-mahoney-3497502?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=frasier-reboot-will-pay-tribute-to-late-john-mahoneyAdam Starkey Wed, 13 Sep 2023 15:45:33 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3497502 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#039;Frasier&#039;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The actor, who played Martin Crane, died in 2018</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/frasier-reboot-will-pay-tribute-to-late-john-mahoney-3497502">&#39;Frasier&#39; reboot will pay tribute to late John Mahoney</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#039;Frasier&#039;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1_Frasier_Enviro_Frasier_010_RT-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> A director on the upcoming <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/frasier"><em>Frasier</em></a> reboot has detailed how the show will honour John Mahoney following his death.</p><p> The actor, who played Frasier&#39;s father Martin Crane across the original show from 1993 to 2004, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/tributes-paid-frasier-legend-john-mahoney-dies-2237225">died at the age of 77 in 2018</a> due to complications from throat cancer.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/which-streaming-platform-is-best-uk-netflix-cancel-now-amazon-shudder-3385131">The best UK streaming platforms – ranked!</a></strong></li></ul><p> In the pilot episode of the upcoming reboot, which sees <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelsey-grammer">Kelsey Grammer</a> return in the title role, Mahoney&#39;s character receives a special tribute.</p><p> “It&#39;s a wonderful scene at the end of the show,” director James Burrows, who helmed the first two episodes of the revival, told <a href="https://ew.com/tv/frasier-preview-kelsey-grammer-james-burrows/?utm_campaign=entertainmentweekly_entertainmentweekly&amp;utm_content=photo&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_term={{.ShareRef}}&amp;fbclid=IwAR37ZL8Drd1q2NgB7smW8wo_9GacKSqJbS9y3rLzqbR0ZVKnGLd66vbP-Lc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Entertainment Weekly</em></a> . “It&#39;s about two-and-a-half, three minutes without any laughs. You&#39;ve got to be brave to do that.”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> He was my father. I loved him. <a href="https://t.co/3mGcyEMxoy">pic.twitter.com/3mGcyEMxoy</a></p><p> — Kelsey Grammer (@KelseyGrammer) <a href="https://twitter.com/KelseyGrammer/status/961302172389355520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 7, 2018</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> The actor&#39;s legacy also lives on in the reboot&#39;s neighbourhood bar, which is named Mahoney&#39;s.</p><p> Burrows detailed how Frasier&#39;s relationship with his son Freddy (Jack Cutmore-Scott) in the reboot attempts to “tap into” the same dynamic between Kelsey and Mahoney on the original show.</p><p> “There&#39;s a lot of Martin in Freddy,” Burrows said. “[Showrunners] Joe [Cristalli] and Chris [Harris] specifically wanted Frasier to deal with his son… because the relationship with Kelsey and Mahoney was wonderful. So they tried to tap into that, and I think they succeeded.”</p><p> The reboot&#39;s cast also includes Nicholas Lyndhurst as university professor Alan, Toks Olagundoye as Alan&#39;s colleague Olivia, Jess Salgueiro as Freddy&#39;s roommate Eve, and Anders Keith as Frasier&#39;s nephew David.</p><p> Alongside Grammer, Bebe Neuwirth and Peri Gilpin also reprise their roles, Lilith and Roz respectively, from the original series.</p><p> <em>Frasier</em> premieres October 12 in the US and October 13 in the UK on <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">Paramount+</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/frasier-reboot-will-pay-tribute-to-late-john-mahoney-3497502">&#39;Frasier&#39; reboot will pay tribute to late John Mahoney</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
